('senior-systems-architect', 'Senior Systems Architect', 'Architecte Systèmes Senior', 'Enterprise Systems', 'Accra / Remote', true, 'full_time', 'Lead architecture reviews and shape high-dependability digital platforms for institutional clients.', 'Diriger les revues d''architecture et concevoir des plateformes numériques fiables pour les institutions.', '["Lead architecture reviews for client programmes","Translate institutional requirements into secure system designs","Set delivery standards for backend, data, and integration work","Coach engineers through critical implementation decisions"]', '["8+ years building production systems","Strong systems architecture and database design judgement","Experience with regulated or mission-critical environments","Clear written and executive communication"]', 'Above-market base for Ghana with project success incentives and Labs upside for exceptional contributors.', 'Path to Principal Architect or Delivery CTO for major institutional programmes.', '["National-scale portal modernization","Digital systems audit for a regulated enterprise","Secure workflow platform for multi-stakeholder operations"]', 'Small senior delivery team with engineering, product, advisory, and client strategy leads.', 'Application review, architecture discussion, practical systems exercise, and final leadership conversation.', 'Q3 2026', true, NOW()),
('senior-backend-engineer', 'Senior Backend Engineer', 'Ingénieur Backend Senior', 'Engineering', 'Accra / Remote', true, 'full_time', 'Build national-scale systems in Go and PostgreSQL. Work on the client portal, APIs, and infrastructure.', 'Construire des systèmes à l''échelle nationale en Go et PostgreSQL. Travailler sur le portail client, les API et l''infrastructure.', '["Design and implement high-performance APIs","Optimize PostgreSQL queries and schema","Own integrations with partner and client systems","Mentor mid-level engineers through production delivery"]', '["5+ years backend engineering experience","Strong Go or comparable systems-language experience","Deep SQL and data-modeling skill","Comfort owning features from design to observability"]', 'Above-market for Ghana with project bonuses and Labs spin-out participation for exceptional contributors.', 'Path to Staff Engineer or Engineering Lead within 24 months.', '["Client portal workflow engine","Billing, notification, and reporting APIs","Audit-ready data pipelines for institutional clients"]', 'Backend team embedded with product, design, and advisory leads on high-stakes client systems.', 'Application review, technical interview, code/design exercise, and final team conversation.', 'Immediate to Q3 2026', true, NOW()),
('product-designer', 'Product Designer', 'Designer Produit', 'Design', 'Accra / Remote', true, 'full_time', 'Design interfaces for platforms that governments, enterprises, and partner teams use every day.', 'Concevoir les interfaces de plateformes utilisées chaque jour par les gouvernements, entreprises et partenaires.', '["Own design system evolution across marketing and portal surfaces","Prototype complex workflows before engineering build","Conduct research with operators, executives, and field users","Partner with engineers until shipped UI feels polished"]', '["4+ years product design experience","Strong Figma and interaction prototyping practice","Design systems experience","Portfolio showing shipped operational or B2B products"]', 'Competitive base plus project bonuses for high-impact launches.', 'Path to Lead Designer or Design Director as the product system matures.', '["Admin portal IA and navigation redesign","Role-based dashboard workflow","Applicant and partner intake surfaces"]', 'Design works directly with engineering and client strategy rather than as a separate handoff layer.', 'Portfolio review, product critique, working session, and final team conversation.', 'Q3 2026', true, NOW()),
('ai-ml-engineer', 'AI / ML Engineer', 'Ingénieur IA / ML', 'Labs', 'Accra / Remote', true, 'full_time', 'Build document intelligence, predictive analytics, and copilots for national-scale platforms.', 'Construire l''intelligence documentaire, l''analyse prédictive et les copilotes pour des plateformes à l''échelle nationale.', '["Design reliable ML and retrieval pipelines","Deploy models and evaluation loops in production","Turn ambiguous client data into measurable product capabilities","Collaborate with domain experts and platform engineers"]', '["3+ years ML engineering experience","Python plus PyTorch, TensorFlow, or modern LLM tooling","MLOps or production evaluation experience","Strong product judgement around AI safety and reliability"]', 'Above-market base plus Labs equity participation for durable product contributions.', 'Path to Principal Scientist, Applied AI Lead, or Labs CTO.', '["Document intelligence for RFP review","Knowledge retrieval for client workspaces","Operational forecasting for delivery teams"]', 'Labs team builds reusable product capability from patterns discovered in client work.', 'Application review, ML systems conversation, practical evaluation exercise, and final Labs discussion.', 'Q3 to Q4 2026', true, NOW()),
('implementation-project-manager', 'Implementation Project Manager', 'Chef de Projet Implémentation', 'Delivery', 'Accra / Hybrid', true, 'contract', 'Coordinate client delivery across advisory, design, and engineering so institutional systems land cleanly.', 'Coordonner la livraison client entre conseil, design et ingénierie pour réussir les systèmes institutionnels.', '["Run delivery rituals across client and internal teams","Track risks, decisions, dependencies, and executive updates","Protect scope while keeping momentum","Translate ambiguity into crisp next actions"]', '["5+ years project or programme management experience","Experience with software delivery or digital transformation","Excellent written updates and stakeholder management","Calm operating style under pressure"]', 'Contract retainer with milestone bonuses for delivery outcomes.', 'Path to Programme Lead on larger public-sector or enterprise portfolios.', '["Government workflow modernization","Enterprise data platform rollout","Partner onboarding programme"]', 'Delivery sits close to the founder, engineering leads, and client executives.', 'Application review, delivery scenario discussion, writing sample, and final leadership conversation.', 'Q3 2026', true, NOW())
